TEXT 1864 -328 Left 2 !.SUBCKT BAT85 1 2\n*\n* The resistor R1 does not reflect\n* a physical device. Instead it\n* improves modeling in the reverse\n* mode of operation.\n*\nD1 1 2 BAT85\nR1 1 2 5.416E+7 \n* \n.MODEL BAT85 D \n+ IS = 2.076E-7 \n+ N = 1.023 \n+ BV = 33 \n+ IBV = 10E-6 \n+ RS = 2.326 \n+ CJO = 1.21E-11 \n+ VJ = 0.1319 \n+ M = 0.2904 \n+ EG = 0.69 \n+ XTI = 2 \n.ENDS
